node-red-contrib-thermoservice (1.0.0-2) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Install to /usr/share/node-red/node_modules/ so node-red palette loader
    discovers nodes automatically (was /usr/share/nodejs/ — wrong path).
  * Remove npm build step: thermoservice.js uses only node:http and node:https
    (built-in modules), no external runtime deps needed.
  * Remove nodejs/npm from Build-Depends.
  * Add postinst/postrm for daemon-reload + try-restart node-red.

